libsource.description: coaxial connector (BNC, SMA, SMB, SMC, Cinch/RCA, LEMO, ...)
coaxial connector (BNC, SMA, SMB, SMC, Cinch/RCA, LEMO, ...)
Generic connector, double row, 02x05, odd/even pin numbering scheme (row 1 odd numbers, row 2 even numbers), script generated (kicad-library-utils/schlib/autogen/connector/)
ARM Cortex-M3 MCU, 128KB flash, 20KB RAM, 72MHz, 2-3.6V, 37 GPIO, LQFP-48
Very low capacitance ESD protection diode, 2 data-line, SOT-23-6
Four pin crystal, GND on pins 2 and 4
100mA Low Dropout Voltage Regulator, Fixed Output, SOT89
High Efficiency Synchronous Buck Converter, Adjustable Output 0.6V-5.5V, 2A, SOT-23-5
